---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Debris Removal | McNadoes Tornado Services"
  description="McNadoes debris removal services deploy AI-commanded tornadoes to clear post-storm, post-demolition, or large-scale commercial sites. Sites up to 500 acres. Timeline: hours, not weeks."
  canonicalPath="/services/debris-removal"
>

  <section class="bg-navy-bg text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gold/70 tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Services / Debris Removal</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Debris Removal</h1>
      <p class="text-mist/70 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Post-event site clearing at atmospheric scale. We command a tornado to your site. It removes the debris. What used to take three weeks and a fleet of excavators now takes forty-five minutes and a direct order.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-blue text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
      {[
        ["500 ac", "Max Site Size"],
        ["±0.3km", "Deployment Accuracy"],
        ["45 min", "Avg. Clearance Time"],
        ["100%", "Post-Service Documentation"],
      ].map(([stat, label]) => (
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">{stat}</div>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white/70 mt-1 uppercase tracking-wide">{label}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-offwhite py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 text-steel leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          McNadoes debris removal operates on timelines that conventional equipment cannot match. Where a standard crew requires two to three weeks for large-scale clearance, McNadoes completes comparable scope in hours. This is not an exaggeration for marketing purposes. It is a property of the service.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our AI guidance platform assesses site topography, debris composition, and prevailing atmospheric conditions to determine optimal tornado classification, approach vector, and dwell time. The tornado is deployed to the site. It does what tornadoes do to debris, except we have told it exactly where to go and when to stop.
        </p>
        <p>
          Post-clearance, our operations team conducts aerial documentation of the site confirming scope completion. Compliant material segregation is included in all debris removal contracts — we know what the EPA requires, and the tornado knows which direction we told it to take the material.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy pt-4">What Qualifies</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {[
            "Post-storm commercial and residential site clearing",
            "Post-demolition material removal",
            "Agricultural field clearing (pre-season)",
            "Industrial site decommissioning",
            "Municipal land clearing contracts",
            "Construction site preparation (see also: Site Excavation)",
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
              <span class="text-sm">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy pt-4">What Does Not Qualify</h2>
        <p class="text-sm">Residential leaf removal. Pool cleaning. Anything described to us as "just a small pile." Please review our <a href="/will-not" class="text-blue hover:text-blue-light">use policy</a> before submitting a project inquiry.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="bg-navy text-white p-5 rounded-sm">
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gold/70 tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Service Specifications</div>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-xs">
            {[
              ["Site capacity", "Up to 500 acres"],
              ["Deployment accuracy", "Sub-kilometer (AI guided)"],
              ["Average clearance", "45 min – 4 hrs"],
              ["Material handling", "Compliant segregation"],
              ["Documentation", "Post-service aerial survey"],
              ["Scheduling", "Subject to atmospheric availability"],
              ["Availability", "See current booking"],
            ].map(([label, value]) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
                <span class="text-mist/50 font-mono">{label}</span>
                <span class="text-mist font-mono text-right">{value}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gold/10 border border-gold/30 p-4 rounded-sm text-xs font-mono text-navy/70 leading-relaxed">
          McNadoes is currently booked through <a href="/" class="underline">the next available quarter</a>. Standard intake is not open. Documented emergency scope may qualify for hardship review.
        </div>

        <a href="/contact" class="block bg-blue text-white text-center py-3 px-5 font-bold hover:bg-blue-light transition-colors rounded-sm text-sm">
          Submit a Project Inquiry
        </a>
        <a href="/hardship" class="block bg-white border border-mist text-navy text-center py-3 px-5 font-semibold hover:border-blue/30 transition-colors rounded-sm text-sm">
          Hardship Review Application
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold">View the full service catalog.</p>
        <p class="text-mist/60 text-sm mt-1">McNadoes offers six core service lines across municipal, commercial, and agricultural applications.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/services" class="px-6 py-3 border border-gold text-gold font-bold hover:bg-gold hover:text-navy transition-colors rounded-sm flex-shrink-0 text-sm">
        All Services →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
